<HL>
   Stamford Capital
   Dissolves Boutique
   Of Lehman Alumni
   ----
   By Michael Siconolfi
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/25/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C12
</SO>
